{"tid":2198182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南美哥倫比亞暴動 有人在狗屋內拘留期間死亡 全國53間狗屋被破壞","createTime":"2020-09-11T07:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T08:00:24.000Z","uid":44209,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"04863d679fddb53c613728b0b37435f80a63664e","tid":2198182,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"哥倫比亞警方表示，蔓延多處的暴力示威，持續兩晚，造成7死、148人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警察總局副局長莫雷諾表示，除首都波哥大出現死亡外，周邊的昆迪納馬卡省亦有人死亡。全國53家警察局被破壞，數十輛警車被毀。波哥大有70多輛巴士遭打砸或焚燒，多家銀行、商鋪等受破壞。約70人因涉嫌破壞公共財產和襲警被捕，傷者包括多名警察及平民。<br />\n<br />\n一名男子日前在波哥大涉嫌違反防疫規定和禁酒令，遭警察暴力執法後死亡。兩名涉事警察被停職並接受調查，但波哥大等地爆發暴力示威。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jPZZBHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjPZZBHY.jpg&h=fbef7fb9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/edbEBHZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FedbEBHZ.jpg&h=cb1f3be2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XqUVUu9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXqUVUu9.png&h=104b75d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8ec642c83378531731ae7b75242370a4a05aa83e","tid":2198182,"uid":30084,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"香港人 : 口屌黑警死全家!! 買蘋果!!! 抗爭左!!"},{"pid":"50c201c4fe4ff59cf3efd83210a6118e5990d0a6","tid":2198182,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"個邊d狗廢<br />\n黑社會仲勁過狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fce3d564372a751700ac7eadc376c279d03fbe","tid":2198182,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50c201c4fe4ff59cf3efd83210a6118e5990d0a6","tid":2198182,"uid":53413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"個邊d狗廢<br />\n黑社會仲勁過狗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T07:24: